import React, { Component } from "react";
import * as customer from "./Customer.style";
export default class Customer extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <customer.Container>
        <customer.Form>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>First Name :</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Last Name :</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Email :</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Phone :</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Address :</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>City:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>State:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Zip Code:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Country:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Company:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
          <customer.InputContainer>
            <customer.LabelContainer>
              <customer.Label>Comments:</customer.Label>
            </customer.LabelContainer>
            <customer.InputMain>
              <customer.Input />
            </customer.InputMain>
          </customer.InputContainer>
        </customer.Form>
      </customer.Container>
    );
  }
}
